  <brief_title>Cortisol Activity in Patients With Prader-Willi Syndrome and Healthy Controls</brief_title>
  <official_title>11 Beta Hydroxysteroid Dehydrogenase 1 (11-beta HSD 1) Activity in Patients With Prader-Willi Syndrome and in Healthy Controls</official_title>
  <sponsors>
