  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to find out if people with Prader-Willi syndrome have a
      difference in the protein which changes inactive cortisone to the active stress hormone
      cortisol.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
